            <title>GoGoX 財團獲發的士車隊牌照　將啟動 300 輛車並招募高達 600 名司機</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/06/gogox-with-taxi-fleet-licence/life-tech/smartcity/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=gogox-with-taxi-fleet-licence</link>
